-ly: (adj) {B1} {tv, radio and news} реальный, живой, {B1} {music} = given or made when people are watching, not recorded; {C1} {engineering} под напряжением, {C1} {healthcare} жизненный = a live vaccine contains viruses or bacteria that are living, {C1} {phones, email and the internet} живой = functioning correctly, so that is connected to another document or page on the internet; (adj) {B2} {personal qualities} = full of life and energy, живой, оживленный; (adv) оживленно, весело